*  088 - Recursive function: Fibonacci (from dotnet)
        DEFINE('fib(n)')                                            :(fib_end)
fib     LE(n, 1)                                                   :S(base)
        fib = fib(n - 1) + fib(n - 2)                             :(RETURN)
base    fib = n                                                    :(RETURN)
fib_end
        OUTPUT = fib(0)
        OUTPUT = fib(1)
        OUTPUT = fib(6)
        OUTPUT = fib(10)
END
